*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
* vim: tabstop=8 expandtab shiftwidth=4 softtabstop=4
* Test tempo ramp (accelerando and ritardando).
* Uses --midi and --fluidsynth output to verify interpolated tempo changes.
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
key     c        $$ 0 sharps
tempo   60,4
meter   4/4
voice   1
bars    12
clef    treble
*-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
instrument 1 Flute            $$ 74   Flauti.
intensity   1     120
pan         1     51
reverb      1     52
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
bars    12
volumes f
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Measures 1-4: steady tempo at 60 BPM
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
measure 1
v1: 4c4, 4d4, 4e4, 4f4
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
measure 2
v1: 4g4, 4a4, 4b4, 5c4
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
measure 3
v1: 5d4, 5e4, 5f4, 5g4
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
measure 4
v1: 5a4, 5b4, 6c4, 5b4
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Measure 5: accelerando target -- ramp from 60 to 120 over measures 1-5.
* Intermediate measures should get: m2=75, m3=90, m4=105, m5=120.
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
measure 5
tempo   120,4,accel
v1: 5a4, 5g4, 5f4, 5e4
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Measure 6: instant tempo change to 100 BPM (no ramp)
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
measure 6
tempo   100,4
v1: 5d4, 5c4, 4b4, 4a4
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Measures 7-8: steady at 100 BPM
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
measure 7
v1: 4g4, 4f4, 4e4, 4d4
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
measure 8
v1: 4c4, 4d4, 4e4, 4f4
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Measure 9: ritardando target -- ramp from 100 to 60 over measures 6-9.
* Intermediate measures should get: m7=86.67, m8=73.33, m9=60.
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
measure 9
tempo   60,4,rit
v1: 4g4, 4a4, 4b4, 5c4
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Measure 10: steady at 60 BPM (verify ramp ended)
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
measure 10
v1: 5d4, 5e4, 5f4, 5g4
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Measure 11: ramp using 'ramp' keyword (synonym for accel/rit)
* ramp from 60 to 90 over measures 9-11. m10 should get 75.
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
measure 11
tempo   90,4,ramp
v1: 5a4, 5b4, 6c4, 5b4
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Measure 12: steady at 90 (verify ramp keyword works)
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
measure 12
v1: 5a4, 5g4, 5f4, 5e4
* ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
cstop*
